{"id":"21065","name":"今日好手气","rarity":4,"path":"Elation","desc":"「师妹，你确信无疑？」\n「哼，绝无错漏！」\n「这次的赌注可不止一瓶护手霜哦。」\n「如此简单的游戏…岂会有变数？」\n粉发女孩转过身，拒绝再受其扰。\n「以茶叶浮沉的迹象来看，师妹你该出那张才是。」\n少女抽签，反转出示——\n「呀，我的好手气来了。」\n「再来再来，这绝对不可能……」\n……\n女孩忘了和师姐玩过多少占卜游戏，只记得师姐总愿意陪她重来。\n后来，女孩想要逃离命定的预言，不顾阻挠，去往了罗浮太卜司。\n初到罗浮，她忽然从卜书的夹缝中发现一枚精致的符签，熟悉的笔迹让在异乡的女孩红了眼眶：\n「谁说命运没有第二种可能？我的转运符，送给你咯~」","icon":"icon/light_cone/21065.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/21065.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/21065.png","ranks":{"id":"21065","skill":"抉择","desc":"使装备者的暴击率提高#1[i]%。装备者施放欢愉技时，欢愉度提高#2[i]%，该效果最多叠加#3[i]次。","params":[[0.12,0.12,2],[0.14,0.14,2],[0.16,0.16,2],[0.18,0.18,2],[0.2,0.2,2]],"properties":[[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.12}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.14}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.16}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.18}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.2}]]},"promotions":{"id":"21065","values":[{"hp":{"base":43.2,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":24,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":18,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":95.04,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":52.8,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":39.6,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":164.16,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":91.2,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":68.4,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":233.28,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":129.6,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":97.2,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":302.4,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":168,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":126,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":371.52,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":206.4,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":154.8,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":440.64,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":244.8,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":183.6,"step":2.7}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":4000},{"id":"116001","num":5}],[{"id":"2","num":8000},{"id":"110261","num":3},{"id":"116001","num":10}],[{"id":"2","num":16000},{"id":"110262","num":3},{"id":"116002","num":6}],[{"id":"2","num":40000},{"id":"110262","num":6},{"id":"116002","num":9}],[{"id":"2","num":80000},{"id":"110263","num":4},{"id":"116003","num":5}],[{"id":"2","num":160000},{"id":"110263